{"tid":734981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有外表沒腦袋全部開除！F1賽車女郎：女權團體別鬧了！　","createTime":"2018-07-09T06:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T08:32:51.000Z","uid":26769,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a86e9951df7d008bac9643217053944881392ef5","tid":734981,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:20:04.000Z","msg":"F1一級方程式賽車近日宣布將在下個賽季正式開除全數賽車女郎，目的在於維護女權主義。但此舉引發眾多失去工作的賽車女郎在社群媒體大聲疾呼自己的工作權益喪失，甚至表示：「請女權團體別再鬧了！」<br />\n<br />\n為了展現在維護女權主義路上有所進展，F1官方表示賽車女郎儘管已經存在多年，但已經不符合目前的世界潮流，同時也與F1的品牌價值不符。<br />\n<br />\n一名賽車女郎蜜雪兒表示，許多人士批評賽車女郎有外表卻沒腦袋，只是空有花瓶。事實上許多女郎都對賽車有非常深度的知識以及興趣。而這也是她們獲得工作時的必備專業，她本人甚至會駕駛F1賽車。<br />\n<br />\n許多失去工作的賽車女郎目前希望透過社群媒體的力量捍衛自己的工作權。希望能夠為自己的飯碗做最後一次的爭取。（丁曉祥/綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180202/640_393457931ec69cd78e7066c480cb6fdd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180202%2F640_393457931ec69cd78e7066c480cb6fdd.jpg&h=5b34f505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180202/640_d1a7300130228c4c084cf8c020ed31d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180202%2F640_d1a7300130228c4c084cf8c020ed31d5.jpg&h=f5cea790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180202/640_20e103c34d102d91bdd3d6bf172ff249.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180202%2F640_20e103c34d102d91bdd3d6bf172ff249.jpg&h=ae063a47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180202/640_b6fd7f2bcd676aa183e1e31572a687f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180202%2F640_b6fd7f2bcd676aa183e1e31572a687f0.jpg&h=c028f968&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3adf78078020d3f0d2762897c841ec26